rrweb record-only bundle
=========================

package : rrweb (record build)
version : 2.0.0-alpha.4
file    : recorder.min.js   (upstream name: rrweb-record.min.js)
source  : https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/rrweb@2.0.0-alpha.4/dist/record/rrweb-record.min.js
renamed : served as recorder.min.js (NOT "rrweb-record") so Brave/uBlock
          tracker filter lists, which match the substring "rrweb", don't block
          the bundle from loading.
global  : window.rrwebRecord   (the record() function; also exposes
          .addCustomEvent / .takeFullSnapshot / .freezePage)

Self-hosted per project convention (no runtime CDN — same as htmx / Chart.js).
Only the record half of rrweb is vendored; replay (rrweb-player) is a dev-only
tool and is intentionally NOT shipped to the browser.

To upgrade: re-download the same path at the new version and bump this file.
